headline: Could Buying UPS Today Set You Up for Life?
summary: UPS' strategy of shifting revenue to higher-margin deliveries and optimizing its network can add significant value for investors.  The stock has enormous potential to deliver great returns for investors, but investors need to be aware of the near-term risk.  Can buying UPS stock set you up for life?
